title: Just Falafel
typeOfFood: Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Part of international franchise, this outlet opened in 2014 as all-veg but added meat in 2015. Offers falafel sandwiches and meals in different flavors, plus some salads. Dairy is used, so vegans should specify. Mostly take-out with seating upstairs.
